			</div>

			<div>
				<img src="css/font/icons8_paper_plane.ico" alt="">
				<h3>Send Information</h3>
				<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. In sed quibusdam, omnis et nisi voluptas. Vero veri.</p>
			</div>

			<div>
				<img src="css/font/icons8_padlock.ico" alt="">
				<h3>Verify Listing & Start Working With Foodies</h3>
				<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. In sed quibusdam, omnis et nisi voluptas. Vero verita.</p>
			</div>


		</div>
	</div>
</div>


</body>
</html>